    <item>
      <title>Re: The Importance of Stats</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=DevCorner&amp;message.id=13473#M13473</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;CLASS: Bard&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;HP:&amp;nbsp; This is a very important part of a bard...People say bards shouldn't get hit when they are soloing,&amp;nbsp; If your kiting a caster&amp;nbsp; you need the HP.&lt;BR&gt;Mana: Well, In the beginning when EQ started I would of said no this is not a very important comodity to us bards. But actually it is very crutial for us as we get higher in level. Also if we are a charm kiter.&lt;BR&gt;Endurance: It's not&amp;nbsp;our biggest worry.&lt;BR&gt;AC: This needs to be high because again we need it for kiting but also in raids/groups. Higher AC we don't get hit as hard.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;HP Regen: This is very crutial.&amp;nbsp; It's something that all classes really need IMO&lt;BR&gt;Mana Regen: This, It doesn't need to be super super high like a caster but it is still needed. I mean we do have an AA that cost 900 mana each time we use it.&lt;BR&gt;Endurance Regen: It's not our biggest worry.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Strength: This is actually something we do need. We are a melee class and we do tend to carry a lot of stuff for our class. Instruments etc. So if we add the weight of all that and if we have loots also, strength is very well needed.&lt;BR&gt;Stamina: This is a HP raiser mostly for us so yes. Any extra HP we can get it's good.&lt;BR&gt;Agility: We need it because of our dodge and that.&lt;BR&gt;Dexterity: This is probably our most crutial stat when it comes to the STR DEX etc. Dexterity is what helps play our songs. Less missed notes and things like that.&lt;BR&gt;Charisma: Now this, A lot of people will disagree with me on. I think Charisma is a very crutial part of the bards stats also. For charming mostly. It doesn't really make the charm last longer but it does lessin your aggro if you are in a group and you charmed something.&lt;BR&gt;Intelligence: We are considered a INT&amp;nbsp;class so it's something we need. It helps us with our song base.&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;Wisdom: Not really the most of importance to us. I guess we can use it.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Cold Resist: When it comes to resistances we need very high of all of them. We are a Kiting/Soloing/Pulling class. And the higher the resistance we have the better off we are. &lt;BR&gt;Disease Resist: &lt;BR&gt;Poison Resist: &lt;BR&gt;Magic Resist: &lt;BR&gt;Fire Resist: &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Attack: Attack rating is needed for any class that uses melee. The higher it is the more often you will hit the mob.&lt;BR&gt;Delay:&amp;nbsp; This goes along with the attack rating. The faster the weapon the more you will hit the mob also.&lt;BR&gt;Damage: Well we aren't really a DPS class but Damage is good to have to add that extra DPS to the group if we are melee.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Range: Depends what range you are talking about here. Range item...only one that gives us stats we don't need it for a bow or anything. NOw if you are talking for other uses like&amp;nbsp;song/spell range then yes we need this quite a bit. If we are kiting the farther away the mob is really the better off we are. Less risk of getting hit.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Haste: Faster hitting faster it goes down so it's important.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Combat Effects: This is agian needed for all melees&lt;BR&gt;Shielding: We need shielding yes&lt;BR&gt;Stun Resist: Very much so. Bards get stunned a lot when they are meleeing or if the selo's drops when your kiting and the mobs catch up to you&lt;BR&gt;Strikethrough: Not really&lt;BR&gt;Spell Shield: Nah&lt;BR&gt;Avoidance: We like to avoid everything &lt;BR&gt;Accuracy: Accuracy is needed&lt;BR&gt;DOT Shielding: Meh&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Skill Mods: The skill mods are very needed for our class...that way we don't really need to carry around instruments if the mod is on the item it self.&lt;BR&gt;Click Effects: Well, There are times you wish you didn't have to play your invis song or levi song the whole time so yes a clicky is good for bards also.&lt;BR&gt;Proc Effects: Proc effects up DPS so yes especially if you are meleeing.&lt;BR&gt;Worn Effects: Depends on what it is.&lt;BR&gt;Focus Effects: Depends on what it is.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
