&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Skill Mods: no&lt;BR&gt;Click Effects: sometimes&lt;BR&gt;Proc Effects: no&lt;BR&gt;Worn Effects: no&lt;BR&gt;Focus Effects:no&lt;BR&gt;-------&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
